column1: Ive used this for years! I do think it use to work wonders in the past, I apply it every night and these past 2 times ive ordered it I feel like it does not work as before. I did stop using it for a few months and started to notice spots in my face so I started to apply nightly. I have not noticed any change for the last 4-5 weeks now. It has worked for me in the past so maybe its just me thinking its not working. Will have to take a picture to compare in a few more weeks from now.
